result.formatted_address: 8 Yan King Rd, Tseung Kwan O, Hong Kong
result.name: 牛摩 Wagyu More

reviews.text:
Well, It was quite good and quite cheap for an all you can eat hotpot buffet, it was just 60 HKD for an hour and half price for the beef, I really liked it because of the frozen yougurt and hotpot which is so much better than shabu shabu, the staff didn't say anything but were quite helpful too.
I also found it extremely cute when they put their logo (a cute japanese devil) on their own food.
On the bad side, there are unfortunately no fishballs 😭 and the chocolate ice cream sucks (thats right, they have ice cream, drinks and soda) but that's pretty much why I didn't give it a 5 star. Definitely recommend it.

Excellent place for hot pot and meat lovers.
They provide lot of choices on soup, and different kind of vegetables, meat quality depends on your choice, but overall is in good quality.  And they not only offer meat, but also with seafood options, and free flow on drinks.
They are good that as they refill your meat fast, and will not becomes less and less for each order, staffs are friendly too
No Service, taste no good
Value for money

All you can eat hot-pot restaurant. Choices of (beef & pork only), (beef + pork + shrimp + musse) menu. The first round food was good, and worsen afterwards. Sushi served seems to have been prepared hours ago. Vegetables and other ready-to-eat food was okay. Overall, not bad for daily life but not a place to enjoy food.

result.adr_address: 香港將軍澳欣景路8號
result.name: 牛摩

reviews.text: 說真的，這家店在裝修前，食物和招呼方面都好好的，但是很奇怪，這家店裝修後，各方面都差到一個點，招呼方面，一到門口，那個待應，愛理不理的，一時在跟對講機對話，一時又在問您問题，到您回應她，她又在跟另一個人在講話，所以第一印象已經不太好了，食物方面也比之前少了一些選擇，尚可以的，＂爐"方面的安排也蠻奇怪的，有一些只是4個人1個爐，有些更是6個人用1個爐，可是又有些是1人1爐，真奇怪，可能是點高級一㸃的肉就可以一人一爐吧!其他都算了，最最最最離譜的是，在吃的過程中，居然有＂蟑螂＂從爐邊不斷跑出來，最少有四隻以上，要我們嚇到站起來，待應才懂得走過來問甚麽事，知道後待應非常冷静的通知上司，她的上司立刻指示她們幫我們換桌，弄了一輪之後，就幫我們轉到另一張桌子去，從發生到我們離去，沒有一個人來說過一句對不起或不好意思之類的話，而又最最最可笑的是，當我們離去時，之前那張＂蟑螂"桌已經給了另外一個家庭在吃了，真的後悔沒有拍下照片，將它公諸於世，所以打了那麼大一段字，希望大家真的想去吃的話，真的要三思呀!

呢期都0K不過早一点好些
今日遲左好多想食都冇
晏左吾再加食物
價錢不算貴，食物還可以。
食物水準好，食美國牛小排好味，肉質好肥瘦適中，價錢合理
90分鐘放題正~~
